This section talks about Stack data structure 

Recursion always use stack 
stack structure

.data
    space to store the data
    pointer to the top of the stack(last insearted element)
.operations//the most important ones
    push(x) 
    pop
    peek(index)
`   stackTop()
    isEmptey()
    isFull()    

 can be implemented using array or linked-list
